
Write an Android or iOS application that displays the shopping cart data provided by the 2 JSON files.!

!!!Requirements!!!
• Items in the cart are grouped by their shop!
• Items are shown with images, name, count and price! !

!!!Bonus Points!!!
• Use an Expandable List View or Expandable UITableView!
• Allow user to edit quantity and remember it when the app is reopened !
• We love Test Driven Development, implement some tests with your code! !

!!!Directions!!!
Package the source code into a zip file. It should be build-able with the latest mobile IDEs (Android Studio and Xcode). For Android provide the APK file. !